This paper deals with scaling out OLTP applications, which involves distributed coordination and partitioning of data and operations. This makes it likely to belong to the Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Databases (cs.DB), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-categories.
